title: Slowdraw the Hungry Eskimo
description:
Uploaded for all you Mega64 fans! (The download link is down on the website)
Slowdraw The Hungry Eskimo is a band featuring Garrett, Dave, Tim, and Paul. Their music has been featured in various Mega64 episodes, skits, and advertisements. Their only album was later released for free download on the Mega64 website.
